# Studio API target
#
# Local default is the Vite proxy: `/api/v1` → http://127.0.0.1:8080
# Leave VITE_TL_API_BASE unset for that path.
#
# Override either here or in src/studio.config.js (STUDIO_API_BASE).
# Env wins when set. See README.md "API target".
#
# VITE_TL_API_BASE=http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1
# VITE_TL_API_BASE=https://staging.example/api/v1
# VITE_TL_API_BASE=https://main.example/api/v1
#
# Do not commit credentials. Demo accounts stay outside docs and .env.example.
